"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人嬲嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲以為自己比英國管治緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就算真係比英國人管咪又係二等公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比共產黨統治既支那人 咪又係三等公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4bb5b54af226d862e87d3ce804c6f7b33d442c","tid":177730,"uid":87908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"咁真係有人有其他國籍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf3b4fd68c64c17287e2d342393466f30e76866","tid":177730,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"唔知其他人點諗，但我睇化左樣野<br />\n所謂「國家」其實只係權力既分界線，同野生動物用自己屎尿畫分地盤一樣，本質其實係醜陋既，象徵住人類既自私同自大。<br />\n<br />\n任何強迫人愛國既諗法都只係當權者想鞏固權力既把戲，係純粹既思想強姦。果件野可愛，我自然會愛，果件野可憎，我自然會憎。我叫你鍾意個暗瘡肥婆又得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n之前施永青話環保係「人類弄出來並且地球不需要」既概念，但其實「國家」先係。我諗清呢樣野，就完全冇諗自己係中國人。我鍾意邊個地方，對果個地方有歸屬感感，我就係果度既人。而中國除左醜陋就只有醜陋，毫無可欣賞既地方。"},{"pid":"9ad8858dc397e3891723949b956a86a267040c5c","tid":177730,"uid":44923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:28:25.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 老衲二世 )"},{"pid":"e208e8efe291cf2dd163062a84236bc412b0ad85","tid":177730,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:28:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6a647b34f2ab9367ce2a6a63e3a065b09b00e79","tid":177730,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁真係有人有其他國籍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔會有個國籍香港既人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3f865115b4193bbd0dfd24656a8cbf26c8c238","tid":177730,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人嬲嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲以為自己比英國管治緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就算真係比英國人管咪又係二等公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比共產黨統治既支那人 咪又係三等公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何來三等，願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b4e0ab66bae0d3230c20b9976d5ee7e30286b1","tid":177730,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁真係有人有其他國籍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔會有個國籍香港既人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我愛黨不愛國囉"},{"pid":"44a4bcd80f0dc220da5211b79b6b2108e8be9fc8","tid":177730,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"好簡單啫 <br />\n<br />\n蝗畀過咩著數 80後 90後 ?"},{"pid":"9815ab336a4717a1f0bc7b45e24246bc32bc0dca","tid":177730,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁真係有人有其他國籍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔會有個國籍香港既人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我愛黨不愛國囉</blockquote><br />\n咪撚愛黨啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6830bc912af181b37b061e852bf7577287f3a9e","tid":177730,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好簡單啫 <br />\n<br />\n蝗畀過咩著數 80後 90後 ?</blockquote><